== Translingual ==
=== Noun ===
'''super''' + '''G''' (G is for giant slalom, the word itself means actually Super Giant Slalom, which is true).
1. a alpine skiing discipline featured firstly wide in the WCH 1985. It is faster than the [[giant slalom]], but slower and more technic than the [[downhill]] event.
